<template>
    <video src="../assets/video.mp4" autoplay @ended="overAudio" @play="onPlay"></video>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "myShiPing",
  methods: {
    onPlay() {
      console.log("开始播放")
    },
    overAudio() {
      console.log("播放完毕")
      this.$router.push('/xiangCe')
    }
  },
  mounted() {
    let videoElem = document.querySelector("vi")
    videoElem.addEventListener('canplaythrough', function () { });
  }

}
</script>

<style lang="less" scoped>
video {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  // position: absolute;
}
</style>
